Diéné Diawara (amụrụ n'afọ 1988) bụ onye Mali na-agba bọọlụ basketball na Limoges ABC nke French Ligue Féminine de Basketball

Diawara na-asọ mpi maka otu egwuregwu basketball ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Mali. Na FIBA Africa Championship maka umunwaayi na afọ 2007 na Senegal, o nyeere ndị otu ya aka imeri asọmpi ahụ, na-eme ka ọ ruo eru maka Basketball na afọ 2008 Summer Olympics
Diawara bụkwa onye kachasị rebounder nke asọmpi ahụ
Ọ bụ nwanne nwanyị Lamine Diawara na Nare Diawara.
